==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Snowdrop
<hw>Snow"drop`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
bulbous plant (<spn>Galanthus nivalis</spn>) bearing white flowers,
which often appear while the snow is on the ground. It is cultivated in
gardens for its beauty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Snowdrop tree</b></col>. <cd>See <cref>Silver-bell
tree</cref>, under <er>Silver</er>, <pos>a.</pos></cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snowflake</ent>⟦br⟧
